<br>
“I came to get dress robes, unlike you, I’m not getting second hand ones.”<br>
<br>
“Neither am I. Besides, are you getting measured and fitted next to me?”<br>
<br>
“Yes, what are you afraid of? Are you afraid that I might see you or something?”<br>
<br>
